title: IEEE 34 node islanding with Artificial Neural Network
description: In this example, the use of an artificial neural network (ANN) for islanding detection in an IEEE34 bus system is shown. The example demonstrates the training and testing processes of an artificial neural network (ANN), and its implementation for islanding detection.
